729034f-c.title: Richmond: Jewett Avenue - Catherine Court
729034f-c.text:
(1)
Jewett Avenue, at the S.W. corner of Catherine Court, showing
the St. John's Evangelical lutheran Church. The view is northward.
March 6, 1930.
P. L. Sperr
